{"title_page": "500 Person Sex", "text_new": "{{Infobox film\n| name           = 500 Person Sex\n| image          = 500 Person Sex.jpg\n| image_size     = \n| caption        = Cover to the DVD\n| director       = Yukitsugu Tsuchiya\n| producer       = \n| writer         = \n| narrator       = \n| starring       = \n| music          = \n| cinematography = \n| editing        = \n| studio         = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = May 4, 2006\n| runtime        = 130 minutes\n| country        = [[Japan]]\n| language       = [[Japanese language|Japanese]]\n| budget         = \n| gross          = \n| preceded_by    = \n| followed_by    = \n}}\n\n'''500 Person Sex''' (''500\u4ebaSEX''), also known as ''A Milestone in History!! 500 Person Sex!!'' (\u4eba\u985e\u53f2\u4e0a\u521d!! 500\u4ebaSEX!!) is an award-winning Japanese [[adult video]] produced by SOD Create, a division of [[Soft On Demand]] (SOD), a large group of media companies.\n\n''500 Person Sex'' was released on May 4, 2006<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dmm.co.jp/mono/dvd/-/detail/=/cid=1open0604/ |title=\u4eba\u985e\u53f2\u4e0a\u521d\uff01\uff01\u8d85\u30e4\u30ea\u307e\u304f\u308a\uff01\u30a4\u30ad\u307e\u304f\u308a\uff01500\u4ebaSEX\uff01\uff01 |accessdate=2008-12-10 |language=Japanese |website=[[DMM.co.jp]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122030447/http://www.dmm.co.jp/mono/dvd/-/detail/%3D/cid%3D1open0604 |archivedate=2009-01-22 }}</ref> and features 500 people having sex in the same room.<ref name=\"ethnorotica\">{{cite web|url=http://ethnorotica.com/article/129/500-person-japanese-orgy |title=500 Person Japanese Orgy |accessdate=2009-04-28 |date=June 13, 2006 |website=ethnorotica.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223230940/http://ethnorotica.com/article/129/500-person-japanese-orgy |archivedate=February 23, 2009 }}</ref> The 130 minute video which has been dubbed the \"Biggest group sex orgy video\" was directed by Yukitsugu Tsuchiya (\u571f\u5c4b\u5e78\u55e3).<ref name=\"records\">{{cite web |url=http://www.world-sex-records.com/biggest-group-sex-orgy-video.htm|title=Biggest group sex orgy video|accessdate=2009-04-28|publisher=World Sex Records| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090427165616/http://www.world-sex-records.com/biggest-group-sex-orgy-video.htm| archivedate= 27 April 2009 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n\nDespite the \"orgy\" label, the 250 couples featured in the video have sex only with each other and not with any other couple. The couples, who are described by SOD as students, enter a large studio set up in a warehouse and spend the next two hours in a variety of sexual acts including foreplay, mutual masturbation, oral sex and intercourse. The unique aspect of the production is that each couple performs all the sex acts in a choreographed manner in synchronization with all the other couples.<ref name=\"records\"/> Viewing the massed couples in action, one reviewer had reminiscences of the [[Computer-generated imagery|CGI]] scenes in ''[[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|The Lord of the Rings]]'' movies<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060416A/index5.htm|title=\u3082\u306f\u3084\uff21\uff36\u3092\u8d8a\u3048\u305f\uff21\uff36\uff01SOD\u30af\u30ea\u30a8\u30a4\u30c8|website=allabout.co.jp|last=Otsubo|first=Kemuta|date=April 16, 2006|accessdate=2009-04-27|language=Japanese|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090403071329/http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060416A/index5.htm|archivedate=2009-04-03|url-status=dead}}</ref> while another was reminded of ''[[March of the Penguins]]''.<ref name=\"ethnorotica\"/>\n\n''500 Person Sex'' was the SOD Create entry (with the production code OPEN-0604)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sod.co.jp/demand/avo/grand/g_entry004.html|title=SOD\u30af\u30ea\u30a8\u30a4\u30c8|website=sod.co.jp|accessdate=2009-04-28|language=Japanese|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090502013036/http://www.sod.co.jp/demand/avo/grand/g_entry004.html|archivedate=2009-05-02|url-status=dead}}</ref> in the 2006 [[AV Open]] contest where it received a Special Jury Award.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060712A/index2.htm |title=\u901f\u5831\uff01AV OPEN\u7d50\u679c\u767a\u8868 (Preliminary AV Open results Page 2) |website=allabout.co.jp |last=Otsubo |first=Kemuta |date=July 12, 2006 |accessdate=2008-12-09 |language=Japanese |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129145455/http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060712A/index2.htm |archivedate=January 29, 2009 }}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:2000s pornographic films]]\n[[Category:Japanese erotic films]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox film\n| name           = 500 Person Sex\n| image          = 500 Person Sex.jpg\n| image_size     = \n| caption        = Cover to the DVD\n| director       = Yukitsugu Tsuchiya\n| producer       = \n| writer         = \n| narrator       = \n| starring       = \n| music          = \n| cinematography = \n| editing        = \n| studio         = \n| distributor    = \n| released       = May 4, 2006\n| runtime        = 130 minutes\n| country        = [[Japan]]\n| language       = [[Japanese language|Japanese]]\n| budget         = \n| gross          = \n| preceded_by    = \n| followed_by    = \n}}\n\n'''500 Person Sex''' (''500\u4ebaSEX''), also known as ''A Milestone in History!! 500 Person Sex!!'' (\u4eba\u985e\u53f2\u4e0a\u521d!! 500\u4ebaSEX!!) is an award-winning Japanese [[adult video]] produced by SOD Create, a division of [[Soft On Demand]] (SOD), a large group of media companies.\n\n''500 Person Sex'' was released on May 4, 2006<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dmm.co.jp/mono/dvd/-/detail/=/cid=1open0604/ |title=\u4eba\u985e\u53f2\u4e0a\u521d\uff01\uff01\u8d85\u30e4\u30ea\u307e\u304f\u308a\uff01\u30a4\u30ad\u307e\u304f\u308a\uff01500\u4ebaSEX\uff01\uff01 |accessdate=2008-12-10 |language=Japanese |website=[[DMM.co.jp]] |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122030447/http://www.dmm.co.jp/mono/dvd/-/detail/%3D/cid%3D1open0604 |archivedate=2009-01-22 }}</ref> and features 500 people having sex in the same room.<ref name=\"ethnorotica\">{{cite web|url=http://ethnorotica.com/article/129/500-person-japanese-orgy |title=500 Person Japanese Orgy |accessdate=2009-04-28 |date=June 13, 2006 |website=ethnorotica.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223230940/http://ethnorotica.com/article/129/500-person-japanese-orgy |archivedate=February 23, 2009 }}</ref> The 130 minute video which has been dubbed the \"Biggest group sex orgy video\" was directed by Yukitsugu Tsuchiya (\u571f\u5c4b\u5e78\u55e3).<ref name=\"records\">{{cite web |url=http://www.world-sex-records.com/biggest-group-sex-orgy-video.htm|title=Biggest group sex orgy video|accessdate=2009-04-28|publisher=World Sex Records| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090427165616/http://www.world-sex-records.com/biggest-group-sex-orgy-video.htm| archivedate= 27 April 2009 | url-status= live}}</ref>\n\nDespite the \"orgy\" label, the 250 couples featured in the video have sex only with each other and not with any other couple. The couples, who are described by SOD as students, enter a large studio and spend the next two hours in a variety of sexual acts including foreplay, mutual masturbation, oral sex and intercourse. The unique aspect of the production is that each couple performs all the sex acts in a choreographed manner in synchronization with all the other couples.<ref name=\"records\"/> Viewing the massed couples in action, one reviewer had reminiscences of the [[Computer-generated imagery|CGI]] scenes in ''[[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|The Lord of the Rings]]'' movies<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060416A/index5.htm|title=\u3082\u306f\u3084\uff21\uff36\u3092\u8d8a\u3048\u305f\uff21\uff36\uff01SOD\u30af\u30ea\u30a8\u30a4\u30c8|website=allabout.co.jp|last=Otsubo|first=Kemuta|date=April 16, 2006|accessdate=2009-04-27|language=Japanese|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090403071329/http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060416A/index5.htm|archivedate=2009-04-03|url-status=dead}}</ref> while another was reminded of ''[[March of the Penguins]]''.<ref name=\"ethnorotica\"/>\n\n''500 Person Sex'' was the SOD Create entry (with the production code OPEN-0604)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sod.co.jp/demand/avo/grand/g_entry004.html|title=SOD\u30af\u30ea\u30a8\u30a4\u30c8|website=sod.co.jp|accessdate=2009-04-28|language=Japanese|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090502013036/http://www.sod.co.jp/demand/avo/grand/g_entry004.html|archivedate=2009-05-02|url-status=dead}}</ref> in the 2006 [[AV Open]] contest where it received a Special Jury Award.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060712A/index2.htm |title=\u901f\u5831\uff01AV OPEN\u7d50\u679c\u767a\u8868 (Preliminary AV Open results Page 2) |website=allabout.co.jp |last=Otsubo |first=Kemuta |date=July 12, 2006 |accessdate=2008-12-09 |language=Japanese |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129145455/http://allabout.co.jp/entertainment/adultvideo/closeup/CU20060712A/index2.htm |archivedate=January 29, 2009 }}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:2000s pornographic films]]\n[[Category:Japanese erotic films]]\n", "name_user": "Jossi2", "label": "safe", "comment": "Copyedit (minor)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/500_Person_Sex"}
